A boatload of beloved VeggieTales pals embark on a fun and fresh pirate adventure with their trademark humour and silly songs in The Pirates Who Don't Do Anything -A VeggieTales Movie! Larry the Cucumber, Mr. Lunt and Pa Grape find themselves on the ride of their lives when they are mysteriously whisked back to the time when pirates ruled the high seas. As they help a brave princess rescue her brother from a dastardly pirate villain, they battle evil cheese curls, giant rock monsters and their own fears and become the most unlikely heroes you've ever seen. It's a swashbuckling good time for the whole family!
